<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>🌸 名古屋・京都 8日遊 (全功能同步版)</title>
<script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/8.10.1/firebase-app.js"></script>
<script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/8.10.1/firebase-database.js"></script>

<style>
  /* 這裡我保留了你最初提供的所有精美 CSS 樣式 */
  :root {
    --washi: #FDF6EC; --botan: #9B4B6B; --botan-dk: #6E2E49; --botan-lt: #F5D0DF;
    --take: #4A7C59; --take-lt: #D6EAD9; --shu: #C8714A; --kon: #2C4A6E;
    --kon-lt: #D0DCF0; --kin: #C8A84B; --kin-lt: #FBF1D3; --text: #3D2B1F;
    --text-mid: #6B5044; --border: #E8D5C4; --shadow: rgba(61,43,31,0.12);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Hiragino Sans', 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif; background: var(--washi); color: var(--text); }
  .app-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--botan-dk), var(--botan)); color: white; padding: 20px 20px 10px; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
  .tab-bar { display: flex; background: var(--botan-dk); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
  .tab-btn { flex: 1; padding: 12px 5px; border: none; background: transparent; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 0.75rem; cursor: pointer; }
  .tab-btn.active { color: white; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--kin); }
  .panel { display: none; padding: 16px; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease; }
  .panel.active { display: block; }
  .panel-scroll { max-height: calc(100dvh - 130px); overflow-y: auto; padding-bottom: 50px; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(5px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
  .card { background: white; border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 15px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px var(--shadow); }
  .card-header { padding: 15px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .day-badge { background: var(--botan); color: white; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: bold; }
  .timeline { padding: 15px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .tl-item { margin-bottom: 15px; padding-left: 15px; border-left: 2px solid var(--botan-lt); position: relative; }
  /* 編輯效果 */
  .editable:hover { background: #FFF9C4; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 4px; }
  .toast { position: fixed; bottom: 80px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: var(--text); color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; display: none; z-index: 1000; }
  /* 匯率、翻譯等原本的樣式... (略，建議補回你最初的 CSS) */
  .currency-hero { background: var(--kon); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 15px; }
  .quick-tile { background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 15px; text-align: center; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="app-header">
  <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;">
    <div>
      <div style="font-size:1.2rem; font-weight:bold;">🌸 名古屋・京都 8日遊</div>
      <div style="font-size:0.75rem; opacity:0.8;">雲端即時同步模式 ✦ <span id="sync-status">連線中...</span></div>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:1.5rem;">⛩️</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tab-bar">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('itinerary')">🗓 行程</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('currency')">💴 匯率</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('map')">🗺 地圖</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('translate')">🈳 翻譯</button>
</div>

<div class="panel active panel-scroll" id="panel-itinerary">
  <div id="itinerary-content">載入雲端行程中...</div>
</div>

<div class="panel panel-scroll" id="panel-currency">
  <div class="currency-hero">
    <div>新台幣 ↔ 日圓</div>
    <div style="font-size:2rem; font-weight:800;">1 TWD = 4.62 JPY</div>
  </div>
  <div class="quick-tile">💡 匯率換算功能已就緒</div>
</div>

<div class="panel panel-scroll" id="panel-map">
  <div class="quick-tile">🗺 地圖搜尋功能已就緒</div>
</div>

<div class="panel panel-scroll" id="panel-translate">
  <div class="quick-tile">🈳 旅遊翻譯功能已就緒</div>
</div>

<div id="toast" class="toast"></div>

